00:03.960 --> 00:05.280
Didn't I tell you

00:05.360 --> 00:06.360
Unless it's for someone important

00:06.360 --> 00:07.400
Don't take it out?

00:08.360 --> 00:09.000
Ruo Lan

00:09.960 --> 00:11.360
Think of another way

00:11.760 --> 00:12.640
See if our household

00:12.640 --> 00:13.480
Has any other valuable gifts

00:13.480 --> 00:14.280
We can prepare

00:14.640 --> 00:15.960
You talk big

00:16.000 --> 00:16.840
